data.description: This property in Christmas Lake Village features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and offers a spacious and comfortable living area for your family. The master suite offers a large walk in closet and private bathroom. The back of the house offers a nice, private yard with wooded scenery from the deck and firepit area. This home is being sold with an extra lot next to the property. Christmas Lake Village offers many amenities including three lakes, a Rec Center and Christmas Lake Golf Club & Back 9 Grill.
